Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從大學以外的地方也能學習到東西\N{\fs38}{\fs38}learn things in places that aren't college.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛科了的孩子都會覺得自己不適合上大學\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Every kid who fails a class thinks college isn't for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道什么是逆境\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I know something about adversity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:14:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要用樂觀的精神面對它\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You just gotta face it with optimism.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 老爸 你對鹿樂觀\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Look, Dad, you're optimistic about this deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也對自己的身體狀況樂觀\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You're optimistic about your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對這世界上除了我的所有事情都樂觀\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You're optimistic about everything in this world but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 當然不是了 - 聽著 你得了帕金森癥很糟\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- That's not true. - Look, it sucks that you got Parkinson's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你很好的面對了它\N{\fs38}{\fs38}And it's great the way you've handled it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你經歷那些勵志旅程時\N{\fs38}{\fs38}but this whole inspiring journey that you went on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還小啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}that was my childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說既害怕又難熬\N{\fs38}{\fs38}And it was scary and it was hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想讓你知道 我已經在盡力做到最好了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I just want you to know that I'm... I'm trying to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的希望你能看到\N{\fs38}{\fs38}And I wish you could see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉 Ian我真沒意識到\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm... I'm sorry, Ian, I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們一直在繞圈\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No, we're going around in circles!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但是我們把話說清楚更重要\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yeah, but it's important we get this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們就見過這個爛樹根了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No, we passed by this rotten log before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么它老跟著我\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Why is it after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是它覺得能把你抓走\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Probably because he thinks he can carry you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我知道你現在需要點私人空間\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Okay, I know you need your personal space right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我只能給你十英尺\N{\fs38}{\fs38}but I'm just giving you ten feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 老媽 你干嘛睡地板上\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh, hey, Mom. What are you doing on the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂的 睡眠派對 \N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh, you know, it's a slumber party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你晚上睡得晚了就得睡在\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You stay up late and sleep on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地板上矯正一下你的脊椎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}the floor so you can stabilize your vertebrae.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你要去哪啊 寶貝 - 那啥 你知道的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Were you leaving, honey? - Well, you know how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我還是喜歡睡我自己的床 - 好的 我玩的挺愉快的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- I sleep better in my own bed. - All right, well... I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊 我也是\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yeah. Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 晚會兒見 - 好的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- I'll see you when I see you. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一夜情溜出門可真堅決啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Wow. That was a pretty solid one night stand sneak-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這妞兒將來會傷不少人的心\N{\fs38}{\fs38}That girl's gonna break a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能避免不少尷尬的早午餐\N{\fs38}{\fs38}of hearts and avoid a lot of awkward brunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 昨晚真是糟透了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Ugh, last night was a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你當時什么計劃啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yeah, what was the plan there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想讓Eve跟我談談心就像跟你談心一樣\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I just wanted Eve to open up to me like she opens up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 這事兒你就別想了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Sweetie... that's never gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Eve是青少年 - 我知道\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Eve's a teenager. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪怕是世界上最酷的人\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You could be the coolest person in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是對她來說 你永遠都是老媽\N{\fs38}{\fs38}but to her, you'll always be her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不想和你談論她的生活\N{\fs38}{\fs38}She doesn't want to talk about her life with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽很遜 科學就是這樣表明的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Moms are lame. It's just science.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你醒了啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh. You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過不用的東西就可以不要了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You said we don't keep things we don't use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Graham 這些東西很貴的 你還拿了什么東西\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Graham, this stuff is valuable. What else did you take?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不記得了嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,150塊錢的"激勵"牛仔褲 只是小了兩個碼\N{\fs38}{\fs38}$150 aspirational jeans. They're two sizes too small
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁減肥法后我就能穿上它了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}because I was gonna fit into them after my juice cleanse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 都弄走\N{\fs38}{\fs38}All right, take it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為我們都回不來了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I thought we'd never get back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 但是你做到了 - 妥妥的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- but you did it. - Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是你擔心那雙意大利皮鞋\N{\fs38}{\fs38}If you hadn't been so worried about your Italian shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會花這么久了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}you would have made better time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 另一只鞋子給貓頭鷹搶去做壓寨夫人了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yeah, one of those shoes is now married to an owl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 Ian 你已經好幾個小時不理我了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Come on, Ian, you've been freezing me out for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們能不能 - 我收到信號了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Can we just... - Oh! I got signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩格\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Two bars!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 Reese 是我 我很好\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Hello, Reese? It's me! Oh! I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我整個晚上都試著給你打電話 只是我\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I've been trying to call you all night. It's just that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不 不 一秒前還有兩格信號的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Hello? What... No! No, I had two bars a second ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信號哪去了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Where did the signal go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能找到個地勢高點的地方\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh, if I just can get to a higher ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不定就能收到點信號\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'll be able to get a clearer path to the transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I could get...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有放棄\N{\fs38}{\fs38}He doesn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造革\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh! Synthetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 B計劃 你有什么銀的物件嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Okay, plan B. Do you have any silver fillings?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比我想象中堅強的多\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You know, you're a lot tougher than I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我沒有顧忌到你小時候的心情\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Maybe I didn't notice what you went through as a kid
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你一直都處理的很好\N{\fs38}{\fs38}because you handled it so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:19:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也沒什么大不了的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yeah, the... you know, it's not that big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是因為這個獲得不少同情親熱\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I got a lot of sympathy make outs because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 關于大學的事兒我不再提了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Well, I won't bother you about college anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以自己做主了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You're your own man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就送你去高中舞會\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Now let's get you to the high school dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好的 但是我來開車 - 嗯 好的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Okay, but I'm driving. - Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 這兒 接著 - 啊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Here. Head's up. - Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 這下可好了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Okay... that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你如何努力反抗 終究會走到一個截點\N{\fs38}{\fs38}No matter how hard you try to fight it, you reach a point
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個你不能再強迫你孩子照你意愿行事的截點\N{\fs38}{\fs38}with your kids where you can't force 'em to do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你能留一件\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Okay, you can keep one,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你必須答應我你會玩它\N{\fs38}{\fs38}but you have to promise me you'll play with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿了手杖\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You got the cane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟Eve在一起那個男的是誰\N{\fs38}Who is that guy eve’s with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都跟你說過了 Mike 這種事情你就別操心了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I told you Mike, we've gotta just relax about these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得陪護人能跳舞嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Do you think chaperones are allowed to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我要是動的太少別嫌棄我\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yeah, just don't be offended if I don't move much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我動的太多別嫌棄我\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Don't be offended if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上 他們終會出落的十分出眾\N{\fs38}{\fs38}In fact, they could turn out pretty spectacular.
