Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是 他跳舞可好了呢 - 不是 親愛的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Yeah, he's a good dancer. - No, honey, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他是真的著火了 - 救命\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- he's actually on fire. - Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}Ian\N{\fs38}Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而總有一天 他們會尋路回到你身邊\N{\fs38}{\fs38}And eventually, they'll find a way back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eve 怎么了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Eve, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我到底怎么了 好吧\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Do you wanna tell me what happened? Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是說不定只有我這么想\N{\fs38}{\fs38}But maybe that's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個樂觀主義者\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm an optimist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Worth it.
